OL,3,CCalls for statue of singer Chris Rea
OL,4,Cto be built in Middlesbrough
OL,6,FMiddlesbrough's politicians have got
OL,7,Fbehind a proposal that would see a new
OL,8,Fstatue of the late singer Chris Rea in
OL,9,Fthe town.
OL,11,FLocal musician Jamie Sample has been
OL,12,Fcampaigning for the late Chris Rea,
OL,13,Fwho died in December, to receive a
OL,14,Fpermanent tribute in his hometown, the
OL,15,FLocal Democracy Reporting Service
OL,16,Freports.
OL,18,FMr Sample created an online petition
OL,19,Fand MPs and mayors who represent
OL,20,FMiddlesbrough and beyond have been
OL,21,Fvoicing their support for the ambition.
