OL,3,CCalls for statue of singer Chris Rea
OL,4,Cto be built in Middlesbrough
OL,6,FDuring a radio appearance on Wednesday
OL,7,F(7 January), the local musician voiced
OL,8,Fhow "nice" it would be for the famous
OL,9,Fsinger to receive a statue in a
OL,10,F"prominent" Middlesbrough location,
OL,11,Fhighlighting Linthorpe Road where
OL,12,FRea's old family ice cream shop was
OL,13,Flocated.
