OL,3,CCalls for statue of singer Chris Rea
OL,4,Cto be built in Middlesbrough
OL,6,FLuke Myer, Labour MP for Middlesbrough
OL,7,FSouth and East Cleveland said: "I
OL,8,Fcompletely agree with Jamie that Chris
OL,9,FRea should be honoured with a
OL,10,Fpermanent statue in Middlesbrough, and
OL,11,Fit's clear that many people across
OL,12,FTeesside feel the same. It would be a
OL,13,Ffitting way to recognise his cultural
OL,14,Flegacy and the pride he had in where
OL,15,Fhe came from."
OL,26,@oD@`OUwD@NO]
