OL,3,CCalls for statue of singer Chris Rea
OL,4,Cto be built in Middlesbrough
OL,6,FThe sentiment was shared by Tees
OL,7,FValley Conservative Mayor Ben Houchen,
OL,8,Fwho is said to have described Mr
OL,9,FSample's proposal as a "great idea"
OL,10,Fand offered to work with the council
OL,11,Fand other stakeholders to take the
OL,12,Fproposal forward.
OL,14,FMayor Houchen described the late Rea
OL,15,Fas an "absolute legend", and not just
OL,16,Ffor Middlesbrough, saying that his
OL,17,Fsongs resonate "right across the
OL,18,Fworld".
