OL,3,CCalls for statue of singer Chris Rea
OL,4,Cto be built in Middlesbrough
OL,6,FWhen it comes to how the singer-
OL,7,Fsongwriter could be depicted, Mr
OL,8,FSample highlighted a photo that he had
OL,9,Fseen, where a young Chris was on an
OL,10,Fice cream bike, with Mr Sample
OL,11,Fexplaining how this would highlight
OL,12,FChris' "humble beginnings" and could
OL,13,Fshow other musicians that enough hard
OL,14,Fwork can make dreams a reality.
OL,16,FMr Sample said that if Rea had been a
OL,17,Ffootballer, then he'd have a statue
OL,18,Foutside the Riverside, but was in a
OL,19,Fdifferent position as a singer.
