OL,3,CCalls for statue of singer Chris Rea
OL,4,Cto be built in Middlesbrough
OL,6,FAnother local MP supportive of plans
OL,7,Fis Middlesbrough & Thornaby East's
OL,8,FAndy McDonald. The Labour MP said:
OL,9,F"With Chris' passing before Christmas
OL,10,Fit really brought home to us how well
OL,11,Floved he was in his home town.
OL,13,F"His music has been the soundtrack of
OL,14,Flocal life with the likes of Steel
OL,15,FRiver, Stainsby Girls and Driving Home
OL,16,Ffor Christmas all Teesside anthems so
OL,17,FI think it's entirely appropriate that
OL,18,Fhe be honoured and a statue would be a
OL,19,Ffitting tribute so I wholeheartedly
OL,20,Fsupport the campaign."
OL,26,@qD@AOUuD@AOU|D@VO]
