OL,3,CCalls for statue of singer Chris Rea
OL,4,Cto be built in Middlesbrough
OL,6,FMiddlesbrough Labour Mayor Chris Cooke
OL,7,Fis also a proponent of the suggestion,
OL,8,Fsaying: "Chris Rea is a Middlesbrough
OL,9,Flegend whose impact on music and our
OL,10,Flocal identity can't be overstated.
OL,11,FHis songs carried stories of our town
OL,12,F` and festive journeys back home to it
OL,13,F` all over the world. A statue near
OL,14,FRea's Cafe would be a fitting tribute,
OL,15,Fand I'd fully support looking into how
OL,16,Fwe can bring that forward."
OL,26,@pD@IOUvD@JrrxD@[O]
